title: Episode 88 w/ Gil Green and Spiff TV (Part 1)
itunes:title: Episode 88 w/ Gil Green and Spiff TV (Part 1)
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this part 1 of 2 the guys drink it up with famed music video directors Gil Green and Spiff tv. They discuss the importance of visuals in the music industry and the various artist Gil and Spiff have worked with. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
